<!DOCTYPE html>
<html lang="fr">
<head>
  <meta charset="UTF-8">
  <style>
    @page { size: A4; margin: 1.5cm 2cm; }
    body { font-family: Arial, sans-serif; font-size: 9.5pt; color: #111; line-height: 1.4; }
    table { width: 100%; border-collapse: collapse; }
    h1 { font-size: 14pt; text-align: center; text-transform: uppercase; letter-spacing: 1px; margin: 6px 0 2px 0; color: #1e3a5f; }
    .subtitle { text-align: center; font-size: 9pt; color: #555; margin-bottom: 10px; }
    hr { border: none; border-top: 2px solid #1e3a5f; margin: 8px 0 12px 0; }
    .ref-line { font-size: 8.5pt; color: #888; }
    .lbl { font-size: 8pt; color: #777; text-transform: uppercase; margin-bottom: 2px; }
    .pname { font-weight: bold; font-size: 10pt; }
    .pdetail { font-size: 8.5pt; color: #444; }
    .sec { font-size: 8.5pt; font-weight: bold; color: #1e3a5f; border-left: 3px solid #1e3a5f; padding-left: 6px; margin: 10px 0 4px 0; }
    .amt td { padding: 3px 8px; border-bottom: 1px solid #eee; font-size: 9.5pt; }
    .amt td.r { text-align: right; }
    .amt tr.tot td { font-weight: bold; background: #eef2f7; border-top: 2px solid #1e3a5f; }
    .paid { background: #dcfce7; color: #166534; font-weight: bold; padding: 5px 10px; margin: 8px 0; font-size: 9.5pt; }
    .partial { background: #fef9c3; color: #b45309; font-weight: bold; padding: 5px 10px; margin: 8px 0; font-size: 9.5pt; }
    .sign-box { border: 1px solid #ccc; padding: 10px 14px; font-size: 8.5pt; }
    .legal { font-size: 7.5pt; color: #aaa; margin-top: 10px; border-top: 1px solid #e5e5e5; padding-top: 6px; }
  </style>
</head>
<body>

  <table>
    <tr>
      <td><strong>LeComptoirImmo</strong> — Gestion locative</td>
      <td style="text-align:right;" class="ref-line">
        Réf.&nbsp;{{ payment.id | string | truncate(8, end='') }}
        &nbsp;|&nbsp;{{ payment.updated_at.strftime('%d/%m/%Y') }}
      </td>
    </tr>
  </table>

  <h1>Quittance de loyer</h1>
  <p class="subtitle">{{ payment.period_label }}</p>
  <hr>

  <table style="margin-bottom:10px;">
    <tr>
      <td style="width:50%; vertical-align:top; padding-right:12px; border-right:1px solid #ddd;">
        <div class="lbl">Bailleur</div>
        {% if payment.lease and payment.lease.parent_property %}
        <div class="pname">{{ payment.lease.parent_property.name }}</div>
        <div class="pdetail">{{ payment.lease.parent_property.full_address }}</div>
        {% else %}
        <div class="pname">—</div>
        {% endif %}
      </td>
      <td style="width:50%; vertical-align:top; padding-left:12px;">
        <div class="lbl">Locataire</div>
        <div class="pname">{{ payment.tenant.full_name if payment.tenant else '—' }}</div>
        {% if payment.lease and payment.lease.parent_property %}
        <div class="pdetail">
          Logement : {{ payment.unit.unit_ref if payment.unit else '—' }}
          — {{ payment.lease.parent_property.full_address }}
        </div>
        {% endif %}
      </td>
    </tr>
  </table>

  <div class="sec">Détail du loyer</div>
  <table class="amt">
    <tr><td>Loyer hors charges</td><td class="r">{{ "%.2f" | format(payment.amount_rent | float) }} €</td></tr>
    <tr><td>Charges récupérables</td><td class="r">{{ "%.2f" | format(payment.amount_charges | float) }} €</td></tr>
    {% if payment.amount_apl %}
    <tr><td>Déduction APL (tiers-payant CAF)</td><td class="r">- {{ "%.2f" | format(payment.amount_apl | float) }} €</td></tr>
    {% endif %}
    <tr class="tot"><td>Total dû par le locataire</td><td class="r">{{ "%.2f" | format(payment.amount_due | float) }} €</td></tr>
  </table>

  <div class="sec">Paiement reçu</div>
  <table class="amt">
    <tr><td>Montant encaissé</td><td class="r">{{ "%.2f" | format(payment.amount_paid | float) }} €</td></tr>
    {% if payment.payment_date %}
    <tr><td>Date de réception</td><td class="r">{{ payment.payment_date.strftime('%d/%m/%Y') }}</td></tr>
    {% endif %}
    {% if payment.payment_method %}
    <tr><td>Mode de paiement</td><td class="r">
      {% if payment.payment_method == 'virement' %}Virement bancaire
      {% elif payment.payment_method == 'cheque' %}Chèque
      {% elif payment.payment_method == 'prelevement' %}Prélèvement automatique
      {% else %}Espèces{% endif %}
    </td></tr>
    {% endif %}
    {% if payment.balance > 0 %}
    <tr><td style="color:#b45309;">Solde restant dû</td><td class="r" style="color:#b45309;">{{ "%.2f" | format(payment.balance) }} €</td></tr>
    {% endif %}
  </table>

  {% if payment.status == 'paid' %}
  <div class="paid">Loyer intégralement payé</div>
  {% elif payment.status == 'partial' %}
  <div class="partial">Paiement partiel</div>
  {% endif %}

  <table style="margin-top:10px;">
    <tr>
      <td style="width:55%;"></td>
      <td style="width:45%;">
        <div class="sign-box">
          <strong>Le bailleur</strong><br>
          Date : _______________<br><br>
          Signature :
        </div>
      </td>
    </tr>
  </table>

  <div class="legal">
    Quittance délivrée conformément à l'article 21 de la loi n°89-462 du 6 juillet 1989 tendant à améliorer les rapports locatifs.
    La présente quittance annule tous les reçus établis précédemment pour la même période. Document généré par LeComptoirImmo.
  </div>

</body>
</html>
